data.description: Are you looking for a Spectacular ranch style duplex only steps away from Mill Creek Park in Boardman? Well... Then come on down to 429 Old Shay Lane because the price is right! Super-Deluxe owner suite consists of 2-3 bedrooms, updated kitchen with all new appliances, large living room with fireplace and 2 full baths. There is brand new Life Proof flooring through the entire unit (with the exception of one bedroom), The partially finished full basement features a family room, currently used as a home theater with woodburning fireplace. The second unit has been completely renovated and has one large bedroom, 1 full bath, updated kitchen and a 1st floor laundry. All of the lighting fixtures have been updated to LED in both units as well as the well insulted 3-car mechanics garage, which features newer doors, new openers, and a nice workshop. The current owner will be happy to convey almost everything you see ...But only if the price is right!
